  description:
    English: 'Slimz is the unwanted result of an affair; abandoned by his parents
      at birth, he has lived alone in the jungle for 30 years, knowing nothing of
      the outside world. No wife, no friends.

      

      Although his weapon
      is just a spear, its effectiveness is comparable to an Alien''s gun.

      

      It
      seemed Slimz would be alone for the rest of his life. But luckily, during a
      tiger hunt, he accidentally encounters his kind ambushed at Command Tree. After
      accepting an invitation from the commander, Slimz enthusiastically joins the
      squad. He vows to fight to the death.'
    Vietnamese: "Slimz l\xE0 k\u1EBFt qu\u1EA3 kh\xF4ng mong mu\u1ED1n t\u1EEB h\xE0nh
      vi v\u1EE5ng tr\u1ED9m, anh b\u1ECB b\u1ED1 m\u1EB9 b\u1ECF r\u01A1i ngay t\u1EEB
      khi sinh ra. Anh ta \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u01A1n \u0111\u1ED9c sinh t\u1ED3n trong
      r\u1EEBng trong su\u1ED1t 30 n\u0103m qua m\xE0 kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt g\xEC v\u1EC1
      th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi b\xEAn ngo\xE0i. Kh\xF4ng g\xE1i g\xFA, kh\xF4ng b\u1EA1n
      b\xE8. \nTuy v\u0169 kh\xED c\u1EE7a anh ta ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 m\u1ED9t chi\u1EBFc
      gi\xE1o nh\u01B0ng \u0111\u1ED9 hi\u1EC7u qu\u1EA3 th\xEC c\xF3 th\u1EC3 \u0111\u1EB7t
      ngang h\xE0ng so v\u1EDBi kh\u1EA9u s\xFAng c\u1EE7a Alien. \nT\u01B0\u1EDFng
      ch\u1EEBng Slimz s\u1EBD c\xF4 \u0111\u1ED9c trong su\u1ED1t ph\u1EA7n \u0111\u1EDDi
      c\xF2n l\u1EA1i. Nh\u01B0ng may m\u1EAFn thay trong m\u1ED9t h\xF4m s\u0103n
      h\u1ED5, anh ta v\xF4 t\xECnh g\u1EB7p g\u1EE1 \u0111\u1ED3ng lo\u1EA1i c\u1EE7a
      m\xECnh \u0111ang mai ph\u1EE5c \u1EDF Command Tree. Sau khi nh\u1EADn l\u1EDDi
      m\u1EDDi t\u1EEB ch\u1EC9 huy, Slimz h\u1EE9ng kh\u1EDFi gia nh\u1EADp bi\u1EC7t
      \u0111\u1ED9i. Anh th\u1EC1 s\u1EBD chi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EA7u h\u1EBFt m\xECnh "
